edu.wheaton.simulator.datastructure

Class Field

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wheaton.simulator.datastructure.Field

  • public class Field
extends java.lang.Object
    Field class for modeling variables. The name and type of the field will not be changeable throughout the life of the field. The value of the field will be changeable.
    Author:
    Simon Swenson
